_large.png?m=1630643913", "name": "apple", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1630643913", "title": "Apple", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple", "topics": 23841, "footer": "", "header": "设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。", "title_alternative": "Apple", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913", "stars": 2741, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 184, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"id": 420921, "username": "Aviciii", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Aviciii", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9754dde9b674711f4d5373839a935bd6?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9754dde9b674711f4d5373839a935bd6?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9754dde9b674711f4d5373839a935bd6?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1560307840, "last_modified": 1674114972}, "last_reply_by": "ShadowPower", "last_touched": 1696921097, "title": "只因列表滑动让我第三次 iPhone 转安卓失败了", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/980471", "created": 1696899514, "deleted": 0, "content": "理性讨论 不引战。\r\n\r\n最近 iPhone 摔坏了，买了个三星 S22U,屏幕、续航、10 倍变焦体验都不错，但是系统 UI 还是不行，虽然是 120Hz 屏幕，但是如 B 站，咸鱼等 app ，列表滑动时有严重的掉帧，动画过度也偶尔掉帧，体验极差。\r\n\r\n已经第三次尝试用安卓系统，第一次是小米 6 感觉屏幕不跟手，响应总是慢半拍，当然也包括列表滚动。\r\n为啥这么多年了，列表的滑动体验还这么差？是硬件、系统还是 app 的锅？", "content_rendered": "理性讨论 不引战。<br /><br />最近 iPhone 摔坏了，买了个三星 S22U,屏幕、续航、10 倍变焦体验都不错，但是系统 UI 还是不行，虽然是 120Hz 屏幕，但是如 B 站，咸鱼等 app ，列表滑动时有严重的掉帧，动画过度也偶尔掉帧，体验极差。<br /><br />已经第三次尝试用安卓系统，第一次是小米 6 感觉屏幕不跟手，响应总是慢半拍，当然也包括列表滚动。<br />为啥这么多年了，列表的滑动体验还这么差？是硬件、系统还是 app 的锅？", "last_modified": 1696899858, "replies": 48, "id": 980471}]